        <text>
            <body>
                
                                        <p>Notum sit presentibus et futuris quod ego <persName key="d1e14008" xml:id="d1e138592">Matildis, <app>
                                <lem>
                                    <sic corresp="#A">comissa</sic>
                                </lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B #C #E #a">comitissa</rdg>
                            </app>
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e138600">Grinionis</placeName>
                        </persName>, donavi ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e138603">Fon<lb n="2" break="no"/>teneti</orgName> pro remedio
                        anime mee vineam <app>
                            <lem>
                                <sic corresp="#A #C">quandam</sic>
                            </lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B #E #a">quamdam</rdg>
                        </app> quam ab <persName key="d1e14014" xml:id="d1e138615">Erardo</persName>
                        in vadimoni<lb n="3" break="no"/>um pro novem <surplus corresp="#B #C #E #a">IX</surplus> libris divionensium acceperam, que sita est in <app>
                            <lem wit="#A">parrichia</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B #C #E #a">parrochia</rdg>
                        </app>
                        <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324356" xml:id="d1e138629">
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#A">Signiaci</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B #C #E #a">Saigniaci</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </placeName> tali pac<lb n="4" break="no"/>to quod ex fructu vinee missarum
                        officia celebrabuntur. Quod si quid residui fuerit inde <lb n="5"/> tela
                        emetur unde corporalia fient. Concessi insuper ut prefatam vineam liceat
                        eisdem <lb n="6"/> fratribus quoquomodo <app>
                            <lem>potuerint</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#C">poterunt</rdg>
                        </app>
                        <app>
                            <lem wit="#A">acquirere</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B #C #E #a">adquirere</rdg>
                        </app>. Promiserunt etiam michi predicte ecclesie abbas et monachi <lb n="7"/> quod si memorata vinea redempta fuerit, percepta redemptio tali
                        deputabitur edificio <lb n="8"/> quod sicut supra condictum est in jamdicta
                        ecclesia <app>
                            <lem>divina</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B">||ivina</rdg>
                        </app> celebrabuntur. Hec omnia et universa <lb n="9"/> de quibus <app>
                            <lem>investiti</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#B">investi||</rdg>
                        </app> erant fratres <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e138673">
                            <app>
                                <lem>
                                    <sic corresp="#A">Fontenti</sic>
                                </lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">Fonteñ</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#C">Fonteneteñ</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#E #a">Fontenetenses</rdg>
                            </app>
                        </orgName> die quo hec acta sunt laudavit et concessit <lb n="10"/>
                        <persName key="d1e14020" xml:id="d1e138686">
                            <app>
                                <lem>Odo</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">||do</rdg>
                            </app> comes <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e138693">Grinionis</placeName>
                        </persName>. Hujus rei testes sunt : <persName key="stutzmann_himanis#324623" xml:id="d1e138696">Odo archipresbiter <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324370" xml:id="d1e138698">Tullionis</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14027" xml:id="d1e138701">
                            <app>
                                <lem>Oliverus</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B">||liverius</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#C #E #a">Oliverius</rdg>
                            </app> de <lb n="11"/>
                            <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e138711">Grinione</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14033" xml:id="d1e138715">
                            <app>
                                <lem>Rinerus</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B #C #E #a">Renerius</rdg>
                            </app> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324359" xml:id="d1e138722">Sancta
                                Columba</placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14039" xml:id="d1e138725">Josbertus de
                                <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#98140" xml:id="d1e138727">
                                <app>
                                    <lem>Masiaco</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#B">||asiaco</rdg>
                                </app>
                            </placeName>
                        </persName>, <persName key="d1e14045" xml:id="d1e138734">Galannus
                            prepositus</persName>. Ut autem <lb n="12"/> hoc totum in <app>
                            <lem>perpetuum</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#C">imperpetuum</rdg>
                        </app> ratum habeatur, ego <persName key="d1e14051" xml:id="d1e138745">Matildis comitissa <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324459" xml:id="d1e138747">Grinionis</placeName>
                        </persName> presentem pagi<lb n="13" break="no"/>nam sigillo meo roboravi.
                        Actum anno Verbi incarnati M° <figure rend="trait"/>C° <figure rend="trait"/>XC° <figure rend="trait"/>VI<hi rend="superscript">to</hi>.<note>Date avec
                            traits entre les chiffres pour la justification</note>
                    </p>
                
            </body>
